Package: inkr
Title: Local Access from R to All INKAR Data
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: 
    person("H. Long", "Nguyen", , "long.nguyen@uni-bielefeld.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8878-7386"))
Description: inkr populates a local DuckDB database with all regional data
    from <https://www.inkar.de/> and creates an interface in R to the
    database via DBI.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/RegioHub/inkr, https://regiohub.github.io/inkr/
BugReports: https://github.com/RegioHub/inkr/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports: 
    DBI,
    dplyr,
    duckdb
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
